I was completely dumbfounded when I stumbled upon this work today and saw that despite definitely having seen it before (I recognized the cover) and the tags promising a contender for a personal favorite (defloration, yandere, nakadashi, sole M&F, -ntr, -cheating, -toys, -femdom) I had it neither faved nor saved on my disc, nor even simply bookmarked. So I read it again, and, to my utter disappointment and grief, discovered why I made no effort to secure a way of ever coming back to this shit: there is way too much selfishness in it. It doesn't matter if she says she loves him, her actions prove the opposite to be true. She mind controlled the dude and raped him several times, in a way that was mainly supposed to satisfy HER, with little to no concern about his feelings. She used the poor fuck as a toy, and he is too deep in love to see and/or mind. This has nothing to do with my ideal of a doujinshi, and I feel cucked by how soul-crushingly it under-delivered on its tags' promises.
